The paper deals with parsing document structures, which involves natural language processing (NLP) and computer vision (CV) techniques. Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also mentions the use of weak supervision, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG - Machine Learning) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI - Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper deals with information retrieval (IR) as it involves extracting information from documents.
